items.sentence: I waited all day for somebody to come and help me.
Tom was supposed to have done that three days ago.
Paramedics worked frantically to save Tom\'s life.
Tom lay down in the grass and looked at the stars.
Tom can play the violin much better than Mary can.
I wish I had paid more attention to what Tom said.
I wish Tom would help around the house more often.
I should\'ve never let Tom go swimming by himself.
It really did happen just the way Tom said it did.
Something like this wouldn\'t happen in Australia.
